{"tid":1895141,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"「用家快入」HKBN 香港寬頻免一個月","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T09:34:35.000Z","uid":19055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0fddb0365fdc941a6b75d57dd13d9be4a33b5b","tid":1895141,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"香港寬頻（1310）今日宣布，鑑於肺炎疫情在港蔓延，為許多企業及家庭帶來沉重經濟壓力，集團決定與客戶共渡時艱，向全港所有住宅固網服務客戶 ，即包括家居寬頻、家居電話及IDD月費計劃用戶，以及企業方案 、HKBN JOS及HKBN Cloud客戶豁免一個月服務月費，當中涉及的總額逾1億元。<br />\n<br />\n所有香港寬頻住宅固網服務客戶由下月2日至15日期間，可透過<a href=\"http://www.hkbn.net/ToughTimesTogether\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbn.net%2FToughTimesTogether&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=f9096466\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkbn.net/ToughTimesTogether</a> 或登入「My HKBN App」登記豁免月費 ，每個戶口之上限為200元；商業客戶則要在同一時段內登入上述網址登記豁免，每個商業登記號碼豁免上限為500元。"},{"pid":"0469fd735a06eb8c4bee5a7902e053b0ae3b345d","tid":1895141,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"終於唔當客戶係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6d41fcee207af7160ef7f22f17835d9e116161","tid":1895141,"uid":242427,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"HKBN食屎啦，續約比舊客個價西到，我幫襯HKT平又平過你，服務又好過您，新客仲有禮物"},{"pid":"6dd657dcf3cd33edf08b7861686763bfd3248685","tid":1895141,"uid":152085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eb6d41fcee207af7160ef7f22f17835d9e116161","tid":1895141,"uid":242427,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"HKBN食屎啦，續約比舊客個價西到，我幫襯HKT平又平過你，服務又好過您，新客仲有禮物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"真啊 同我講公屋100M要228 我話你諗清楚再打黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eeebe725db7300596563c332f5f431d769b9df","tid":1895141,"uid":60478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T12:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已